data: The organization Urban Cycling Collective is a GROUP.
The organization Urban Cycling Collective operates in the Recreational Sports industry.
The organization Urban Cycling Collective focuses on promoting safe and sustainable biking in city environments.
The organization Urban Cycling Collective is based in Chicago, Illinois, USA.
The organization Urban Cycling Collective is a grassroots community.
The organization Urban Cycling Collective values safety, community, and sustainability.
The organization Urban Cycling Collective has over 500 members.
